  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Stuart Little 2 is a 2002 platform video game, based on the film of the same name. This is the PlayStation 1 version; a game called \"Stuart Lilttle 2\" also came out on the Game Boy Advance and PC, but all three are different games. The PC and GBA games are primarily 2D side scrolling, but this game is a fully 3D platformer with 6 stages to explore and each has 6 jeweled rings to collect. The rings can be used to unlock further stages.",
